{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "d112bbfb-37b8-4a7b-a96c-fe27b51afef8", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d112bbfb-37b8-4a7b-a96c-fe27b51afef8@1.pkg/1772597606750/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597607644", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d112bbfb-37b8-4a7b-a96c-fe27b51afef8@1.pkg/1772597606750/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597607644"}, "identifier": "d112bbfb-37b8-4a7b-a96c-fe27b51afef8", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>本题考查掌握交友的基本原则。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>A：帮助同学躲避老师的检查，偷带手机进入课堂的行为是错误的，不符合交友的正确原则。因此A错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>B：陪同学翘课去看比赛的行为是错误的，是不遵守校规校纪的做法，也是没有坚持正确原则的体现，因此B错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>C：拒绝同学考试作弊要求帮助的行为，是坚持了原则和底线的体现，故C正确</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>D：破坏共享单车锁具的行为是违法行为，帮其望风也是共犯，因此这种做法是错误的，并没有坚守自身原则。因此D错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>因此选C</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）友谊不能没有原则，当朋友误入歧途，我们需要提醒、规劝甚至替朋友&ldquo;踩刹车&rdquo;。以下情境中的&ldquo;我&rdquo;，坚持了原则的是（ &nbsp; &nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）友谊不能没有原则，当朋友误入歧途，我们需要提醒、规劝甚至替朋友“踩刹车”。以下情境中的“我”，坚持了原则的是（    ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d112bbfb-37b8-4a7b-a96c-fe27b51afef8@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754977936178", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>玲玲偷带手机入课堂，我帮她躲避老师的检查</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>阿明想逃课看球赛，我陪他一起翘课去看比赛</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>小新考试作弊求掩护，我拒绝并劝他诚实应考</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>小杰想破坏共享单车锁具，我替他望风和警戒</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）友谊不能没有原则，当朋友误入歧途，我们需要提醒、规劝甚至替朋友&ldquo;踩刹车&rdquo;。以下情境中的&ldquo;我&rdquo;，坚持了原则的是（ &nbsp; &nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_nc